[126.539678, "o", ";2;232;220;198m  \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;185;192;171m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m 10 \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198mThe new pitch is a near-direct replication of BlockFi's core product: a US consumer-facing digital asset savings account that pays high yield by lending deposits to institutional count\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m  \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;185;192;171m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m    \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198merparties, with tiered rates by lock-up duration and no account fees. The Trusted facts confirm alignment on every major taxonomy dimension —\u001b[35;148H geography (US), customer type (consumer), \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m  \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;185;192;171m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198m    \u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m\u001b[48;2;232;220;198msub-sector (cryptocurrency lending), and monetization model (usage/spread-based). BlockFi's rise and fall is the canonical case study for this exact business.                          \u001b[19;7H\u001b[?2026l"]
